window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>From </b><b><i>Wall Street Journal</i></b><b> and </b><b><i>USA Today </i></b><b>best-selling</b> <b>author M. Robinson comes a standalone best friend’s baby sister, second chance billionaire romance.</b></p> <p>She was my best friend's little sister, which meant she was off limits, but I couldn’t help myself. I never could when it came to her, and in the end, I left town and made something of my myself.</p> <p>Ten years later and I'm one of the richest men in the world. I have everything I ever wanted...except for her.</p> <p>Little did I know, life would give me a second chance to make things right by her. She's now suddenly my publicist, treating me as if I'm nothing more than another client, when <i>I </i>stole all her firsts. Including her heart. I need to take matters into my own hands, so I'm making her an offer she can't refuse.</p> <p> She's signed a contract stating that for the next 10 days…. She's mine.</p>"; 
